# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
# Example: feat(auth): add login validation
# -------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, test, chore, perf, ci, build
# -------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Subject: Use imperative, present tense ("add" not "added")
# Scope: (Optional) noun describing the section of the code
# -------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Body: (Optional) Motivation for the change and contrast with previous behavior.

# Footer: (Optional) Reference issues (e.g., Closes #123)